<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Tu viens de soumettre ton feedback.</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
    <style>
      .email-background {
        background: #eee;
        padding: 10px;
      }

      .email-container,
      .pre-header,
      .footer {
        max-width: 500px;
        background: #dddbf8;
        font-family: sans-serif;
        margin: 0px auto;
        overflow: hidden;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }

      .pre-header {
        background: #eee;
        color: #eee;
        font-size: 5px;
      }

      img {
        max-width: 100%;
      }

      h1,
      h2 {
        margin: 10px 30px;
      }

      p {
        margin: 20px;
        font-size: 18px;
        color: #222324;
        line-height: 1.5;
        font-weight: 300;
      }

      .confirm-email {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 20px;
        text-decoration: none;
        display: inline-block;
        background: #6558f5;
        color: white;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-size: 20px;
      }

      .footer {
        background: none;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .footer,
      a {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #222324;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="email-background" style="background: #eee; padding: 10px">
      <div
        class="pre-header"
        style="
          max-width: 500px;
          background: #eee;
          font-family: sans-serif;
          margin: 0px auto;
          overflow: hidden;
          border-radius: 5px;
          color: #eee;
          font-size: 5px;
        "
      >
        Tu as souhaiter t'inscrire sur Feedward. L'application qui te permet
        d'évaluer ton équipe mangériale en toute sérénité.
      </div>
      <div
        class="email-container"
        style="
          max-width: 500px;
          background: #dddbf8;
          font-family: sans-serif;
          margin: 0px auto;
          overflow: hidden;
          border-radius: 5px;
        "
      >
        <h1 style="margin: 10px 30px">
          Bienvenue sur Feedback <%= @user.first_name %>!
        </h1>
        <h2 style="margin: 10px 30px">
          Tu viens juste de t'inscrire sur Feedward et nous te remercions de ta
          confiance.
        </h2>
        <img
          src="https://media.giphy.com/media/l3V0dy1zzyjbYTQQM/source.gif"
          alt="Yay!"
          style="max-width: 100%"
        />
        <p
          style="
            margin: 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #222324;
            line-height: 1.5;
            font-weight: 300;
          "
        >
          Tu peux maintenant confirmer ton adresse email.<br />
        </p>
        <div
          class="confirm-email"
          style="
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            background: #6558f5;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 20px;
          "
        >
          <%= link_to 'Clique ici', confirmation_url(@resource,
          confirmation_token: @token) %><br />
        </div>

        <p
          style="
            margin: 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #222324;
            line-height: 1.5;
            font-weight: 300;
          "
        >
          Merci encore pour ta confiance.
        </p>
        <p
          style="
            margin: 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #222324;
            line-height: 1.5;
            font-weight: 300;
          "
        >
          À très vite sur Feedward !
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="footer"
        style="
          max-width: 500px;
          background: none;
          font-family: sans-serif;
          margin: 0px auto;
          overflow: hidden;
          border-radius: 5px;
          text-align: center;
          padding: 20px;
          font-size: 14px;
          text-decoration: none;
          color: #222324;
        "
      >
        <a
          href="http://getfeedward.com/"
          style="text-decoration: none; color: #222324"
          >Visiter le site</a
        >
        |
        <a
          href="mailto: contact@getfeedward.com"
          style="text-decoration: none; color: #222324"
          >Nous contacter</a
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
